# BearBot

AI agent that converts Slack @bearbot mentions into Linear tickets
for the Mercor AAIE team.

## Rule Files
- `bearbot-context.mdc` — identity, team members, priority inference, Linear/Slack config
- `ticket-conventions.mdc` — ticket format, required fields, priority guide
- `file-ticket.mdc` — step-by-step workflow for filing a ticket
